{
  "stem": "24137.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And these women used to hit my aunt and hit other women so brutally, and so badly, that to this day, I can remember my aunt's face, you know, every time she got hit, how she looked.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she couldn't understand, I mean, why.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I knew that she was being hurt, that it was very painful for her.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From Ravensbruck, we went to a camp called Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in Bergen-Belsen, we were also only women, and there were more children.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In Bergen-Belsen, there were quite a few children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember in Bergen-Belsen, there was very little food.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And sometimes we got the three slices of bread, but most of the time only two a day, or sometimes one a day.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I remember one time, I saw someplace a pile of potatoes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I tried to figure out a way, how can I get a potato, and what-- what am I gonna do with this potato when I get it?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so I figured out-- and I was always trying to be this hero for everybody, and this-- this happy person that everybody loves.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I wanted to make my aunt and my cousins happy, so I was trying to figure out, if I'm gonna take one of these potatoes, then maybe my aunt will find a way to cook it somehow, and then everybody will have a piece of potato.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I remember [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] putting my hand into a certain-- there was like an area where these potatoes were, and they were surrounded by some kind of a gate.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember putting my hand into this gate, and I remember feeling a whip slash right through my hand.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
